{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "2.880", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "2.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.880", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kollegen und Kolleginnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.400", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Soldatinnen und Soldaten \u00fcben inzwischen nicht mehr nur f\u00fcr einen rein hypothetischen Ernstfall."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das \u00dcben war wegen eventueller Unf\u00e4lle\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde erw\u00e4hnt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.440", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gar nicht so ungef\u00e4hrlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.800", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mittlerweile werden sie von uns, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.440", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem Parlament, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.000", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber immer h\u00e4ufiger in Auslandseins\u00e4tze geschickt und sind dort sehr realen Gefahren ausgesetzt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.960", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Allein im Afghanistan-Einsatz sind bislang 56\u00a0Personen umgekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.280", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir alle wissen und haben es hier auch schon geh\u00f6rt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.520", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr ist seit 2011 nicht l\u00e4nger eine Armee von Wehrpflichtigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.560", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern eine Berufsarmee. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.880", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das schafft Rekrutierungsprobleme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.080", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denen wir aber nicht mit einer verst\u00e4rkten Anwerbung von Minderj\u00e4hrigen begegnen d\u00fcrfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kinderkommission des Deutschen Bundestages hat sich in der letzten Wahlperiode ausf\u00fchrlich mit diesem Thema befasst und empfohlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Mindestalter f\u00fcr den Dienstbeginn von 17 auf 18\u00a0Jahre anzuheben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.080", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich habe gro\u00dfes Verst\u00e4ndnis daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.640", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der Linken ihren Antrag aus der letzten Wahlperiode erneut einbringen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn die Zahl der minderj\u00e4hrigen Rekrutinnen und Rekruten ist wieder gestiegen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.600", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2017 noch \u00fcber die im Antrag genannte Zahl hinaus auf mehr als 2\u00a0100\u00a0minderj\u00e4hrige Rekruten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Wehrbeauftragte hat in seinem Bericht ebenfalls darauf hingewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.280", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Rekrutierung von Minderj\u00e4hrigen eine Ausnahme bleiben muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.000", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Inzwischen ist die Zahl so hoch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass von einer Ausnahme nicht mehr gesprochen werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Besonders bei den jungen Frauen sind die Zuwachsraten gewaltig."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.040", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Kollege Martin Gerster hat darauf hingewiesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.360", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir uns unter den Unterzeichnern des Fakultativprotokolls zur Kinderrechtskonvention in guter Gesellschaft befinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr entspricht den dort eingegangenen Verpflichtungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.240", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem Minderj\u00e4hrige von bewaffneten Konflikten ferngehalten werden und auch keine Wachdienste mit der Waffe leisten d\u00fcrfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dennoch werden sie an der Waffe ausgebildet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.400", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das halte ich f\u00fcr nicht akzeptabel und unverantwortlich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr bietet zweifellos gute Ausbildungen an und ist ein attraktiver Arbeitgeber. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.600", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da die Schulabg\u00e4nger wegen fr\u00fcherer Einschulung und verk\u00fcrzter Schulzeit f\u00fcr Gymnasiasten j\u00fcnger werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.840", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss man sich etwas einfallen lassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.400", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr Jugendliche sind Warteschleifen eben nicht attraktiv. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Darum hat die SPD-Bundestagsfraktion in ihrem Positionspapier vom Juni 2017 vorgeschlagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Minderj\u00e4hrige sollten zun\u00e4chst in ein ziviles Ausbildungsverh\u00e4ltnis bei der Bundeswehr \u00fcbernommen werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.280", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort gibt es zahlreiche Ausbildungsm\u00f6glichkeiten: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Handwerk, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Logistik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.480", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Bereich IT und Elektronik, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.720", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "im Bereich Medizin und Gesundheit und auch im mittleren nichttechnischen oder naturwissenschaftlichen Dienst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.120", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "54\u00a0Ausbildungsberufe in 400 verschiedenen Ausbildungsst\u00e4tten listet die Webseite der Bundeswehr. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.680", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00f6glich w\u00e4re auch ein spezieller Vorbereitungsdienst mit einem eigenen Ausbildungskonzept. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.800", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die \u00dcbernahme in ein milit\u00e4risches Dienstverh\u00e4ltnis folgt dann erst mit der Vollj\u00e4hrigkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.800", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.400", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kommen Sie zum Schluss?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.480", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.800", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich komme zum Ende.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wieder eine Gro\u00dfe Koalition zustande kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.400", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hoffe ich sehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.520", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass meine Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der Union hierzu doch noch Gespr\u00e4chsbereitschaft zeigen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.560", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.080", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.480", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir kommen nun zum letzten Redner zu diesem Tagesordnungspunkt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.000", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege Florian Hahn von der CDU/CSU-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}